{"id": 1024, "genre": 1001, "title": "你还蛮烦综艺节目的什么套路？", "description": "不是套路就是引发尴尬癌，而我还是在看。（题图来自：Pavel Mishkin）", "record_count": 8392, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152318SD3yU9iwCEzovQ1Z.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-31T11:08:46Z", "options": [{"id": 83714, "content": "湖南卫视的所有套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620996}, {"id": 83715, "content": "无意义的剪辑，多次回放", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2095}, {"id": 83716, "content": "动不动就结盟，结个屁盟啊！撕B背叛才是我们的爱啊！！！有没有点儿胜负欲！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2095}, {"id": 84228, "content": "梗出第一遍时是惊喜，第二遍时是回忆，第三遍就成老梗了；而且使用越频繁，观众腻歪的越快", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585982}, {"id": 83717, "content": "煽情", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 629453}, {"id": 83718, "content": "从来没看过综艺节目?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252109}, {"id": 83719, "content": "观众哭的死去活来 明明就唱了一首不温不火的歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191998}, {"id": 83720, "content": "跑男的撕名牌真是够了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628342}, {"id": 83721, "content": "互相抢话说，搞得摄影师很尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456128}, {"id": 84233, "content": "为什么旁白这么多诶，特别蠢！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632432}, {"id": 88841, "content": "抄袭笑点。看完韩国综艺再看中国综艺，尼玛笑点都一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219928}, {"id": 83723, "content": "同一个镜头重复放5次", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628349}, {"id": 83724, "content": "把无知当直率", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628349}, {"id": 84748, "content": "就是感觉很作的时候让人一眼就辨得出 “不可以，这就是综艺。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488255}, {"id": 83725, "content": "刚开始大陆综艺就是仿台湾，现在韩流盛行又开始仿韩，各种套路不绝，也不知道什么时候才能刮起一阵仿大陆风……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563184}, {"id": 115469, "content": "必捧一人，必有人肉背景??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755861}, {"id": 83726, "content": "慢镜头，慢镜头，还是慢镜头，终于，广告了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620475}, {"id": 83727, "content": "博物馆打闹！博物馆打闹！！博物馆打闹！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613988}, {"id": 83728, "content": "就怕矫情，明明不伤感，泪点低的要死。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573948}, {"id": 83730, "content": "不尊重别人感受的行为都是真性情喽", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630419}, {"id": 83731, "content": "满满的尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630430}, {"id": 83732, "content": "浮夸 ，不真实", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 629497}, {"id": 83733, "content": "全部点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311308}, {"id": 83734, "content": "观众太爱演", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529427}, {"id": 89110, "content": "假装关系很好的演技", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646515}, {"id": 83735, "content": "抄！", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611678}, {"id": 83736, "content": "爸爸去哪儿 强行皆大欢喜", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462030}, {"id": 83737, "content": "一副特别努力让节目变得有趣的样子我真的笑不出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630440}, {"id": 83738, "content": "各种借机宣传新戏新电影?", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630444}, {"id": 83739, "content": "各种借机宣传新戏新电影?", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630444}, {"id": 83740, "content": "当原版粉看到开头就能预测到后面所有所谓“笑点”的时候…抄的太彻底…", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 625267}, {"id": 83741, "content": "看看奔跑吧兄弟，就知道了", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 582043}, {"id": 83743, "content": "就是很尴尬 那么作还要装真性情", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584977}, {"id": 83999, "content": "花钱买了版权的，就有钱了不起，连字幕的位置都一模一样；演员、导演、剪辑、道具、植入广告…不会就学学，鄙视观众的智商也要有个底线吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622228}, {"id": 83744, "content": "各种动作回放 各个角度来一遍 特别是已经可以看到结果的动作 你还给我慢回放干嘛！这样有悬念吗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630459}, {"id": 83745, "content": "明明嘉宾的表现差强人意，但其他人却碍于面子或交情硬要撑出笑脸捧场，还要大声叫好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581744}, {"id": 83747, "content": "卖蠢", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 625365}, {"id": 83749, "content": "流泪", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607774}, {"id": 83750, "content": "强行鬼畜", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162040}, {"id": 84262, "content": "一个镜头要重复三遍！一个镜头要重复三遍！一个镜头要重复三遍！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632564}, {"id": 83751, "content": "乱煽情，一季完结时弄得跟生离死别一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290656}, {"id": 83752, "content": "作！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583337}, {"id": 84008, "content": "博物馆撕名牌，还自以为很厉害，全无公德心全无谦卑心，只有做作的恶心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142533}, {"id": 83753, "content": "套路狗啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630486}, {"id": 83754, "content": "一个镜头回放N遍！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150254}, {"id": 83758, "content": "傻乐，看得我很尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585498}, {"id": 83759, "content": "无脑回放……", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628291}, {"id": 83760, "content": "装弱智", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578591}, {"id": 83761, "content": "假", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 418681}, {"id": 83762, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 19741}]}